高等微積分(一)(二)














真理大學應用數學系





科目名稱(中文)：高等微積分(一)(二)
科目名稱(英文)：Advanced Calculus 
開課班級：二年級 
學分數：上、下學期各5學分 
課程綱要: 
本科目包括下列各課題及其應用。教師可依實際狀況做適度調整。 
上學期 
1.      THE REAL LlNE AND EUCLlDEAN SPACE 
1. Least Upper Bounds 2. Cauchy Sequences 3. Cluster Points; lim inf and lim sup 4. Euclidean Space 5. Norms, Inner Products, and Metrics 
2.  THE TOPOLOGY OF EUCLlDEAN SPACE 
1. Open Sets 2. Interior of a Set 3. Closed Sets 4. Accumulation Points 5. Closure of a Set  6. Boundary of a Set 7. Sequences 8. Completeness 
3.  COMPACT AND CONNECTED SETS  
1. Compactness 2. Connected Sets 
4.  CONTINUOUS MAPPINGS (I) 
1. Continuity 2. Images of Compact and Connected Sets 3. Operations on Continuous Mappings. 4. The Boundedness of Continuous Functions on Compact Sets 
 ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
 下學期 
5. CONTINUOUS MAPPINGS (II) 
1. The Intermediate Value Theorem 2. Uniform Continuity 3. Differentiation of Functions of One Variable 4. Integration of Functions of  One Variable 
6. UNIFORM CONVERGENCE 
1. Pointwise and Uniform Convergence 2. The Weierstrass M Test 3. Integration and Differentiation of Series 4. The Elementary Functions 5. The Space of Continuous Functions 6. The Contraction Mapping Principle and Its Applications 7. The Stone-Weierstrass Theorem 8. The Dirichlet and Abel Tests 
7. DIFFERENTIABLE MAPPINGS 
1. Definition of the Derivative 2. Continuity of Diffrentiable Mappings; Differentiable Paths 3. Conditions for Differentiability 4. The Chain Rule 5. The Mean Value Theorem 
8. THE INVERSE AND IMPLlCIT FUNCTION THEOREMS AND RELATED TOPICS 
1. Inverse Function Theorem 2. Implicit Function Theorem 
 
 





 







